{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Create regions from adjacent items across tracks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Creates regions that comprise all items that are less than a given number of seconds (default: 1) apart. The region render matrix gets adjusted to render the respective tracks for the created regions and/or the master track (configurable). Regions are named and colored after track of first item in region.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Evaluates items on selected tracks or all items if no tracks are selected.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Instructions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab modify gap value and render setting in first lines of code (optional)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab select track or tracks (optional)\par}
